{"tid":1405674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB訪問。。。","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:52:12.000Z","uid":63159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f42aabf6ac484bc60a49eb2074769e81af7a9b18","tid":1405674,"uid":63159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"TVB而家做訪問<br />\n支咪會冇咗TVB logo<br />\n反光衣亦唔會有<br />\n所以大家如果比呢啲所謂嘅記者訪問<br />\n首先要知佢係做邊間公司<br />\n同埋記得要對無線新聞做嘅好事表達意見<br />\n由於佢可以做剪接<br />\n所以有標語顯示反對媒體失實一定要展示係鏡頭面前<br />\n<br />\n利申，藍絲家人睇tvb，見到另一個親戚接受tvb訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7412cd7caae584d21c0045b6e51348074554c23","tid":1405674,"uid":63159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"自推，想多啲人留意，因為tvb真係影響好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}